WEBVTT

00:07:58.237 --> 00:08:01.560
Suddenly, those aperture blades
are poking through that reflection

00:08:01.584 --> 00:08:03.369
the way nothing else has.

00:08:03.966 --> 00:08:07.508
Now we recognize WALL-E as having an eye.

00:08:07.532 --> 00:08:10.181
As humans we have the white of our eye,

00:08:10.205 --> 00:08:11.356
the colored iris

00:08:11.380 --> 00:08:12.601
and the black pupil.

00:08:12.948 --> 00:08:16.289
Now WALL-E has the black of an eye,

00:08:16.313 --> 00:08:17.840
the gray aperture blades

00:08:17.864 --> 00:08:19.283
and the black pupil.

00:08:19.689 --> 00:08:23.331
Suddenly, WALL-E feels like he has a soul,

00:08:23.355 --> 00:08:26.233
like there's a character
with emotion inside.

00:08:28.038 --> 00:08:29.855
Later in the movie towards the end,

00:08:29.879 --> 00:08:31.357
WALL-E loses his personality,